{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5ba9b3abcb","title":"关于国家预算的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"38bc04a234","index":0,"year":1954,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949.10-1957.12）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"98d4de7d87","type":"paragraph","text":"青少年的教育","index":0,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"102a8ed2f1","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五三年）","index":1,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"1e31016ef8","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅有一篇女章，题目是“从孩子的照相酰起”，鲁迅很懂得这个事情，他提倡孩子要活，要皮。他“聊良之类井不是恶德，但发展开去，对一切事无不刷良，却决不是美德，也筒直倒是没出息。（《鲁迅全集》第六卷第84页）在有些地方要我们的后一代学我们；但有些地方就决不要后代再学我们，再学我们就槽糕。我们总是中孔夫子的毒太深了，不仅学校如此，就是托儿所也要很好注意。现在不把孩子运到托儿所还好，一送到托儿所就“机械化”了。在这些方面，我何要下很大的功夫，用很多方法，把我们的青年、儿童变成朝气蓬勃，生龙活虎一样。有这样的人民，建立这样一个国家，那我们中国就了不起。要馈得人在幼年、青年的时候，正是性格、品质慢慢形成的时候，如果在这方面不会教育他们，将来的提失就很大。","index":2,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"0f84436e69","type":"paragraph","text":"给李×的一封信××见：","index":3,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"5a7445288f","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十日的借及两篇女章，收到看过了，觉得很好。特别是政治思想一篇对赣者帮助更大。似乎有些错处，例如“实用主义老主张物质的第一性和意的第二性。”此外，在批判实用主义时，对实用主义所酰的实用和效果，和我们所酰的大体同样的名制，需加以比较明，一般人对这些还是混潜不清的。宇宙“是一篇未完的草稿··九句，也须作明的批判。你的交章通俗易懂，这是很好的。在再写女章时，建酸对一些哲学的基本概念，利用适当的场合，加以截明，使一般干部能够看懂。要利用这个机会。使几百万的不懂哲学的党内外干部都懂得一点马克思主义哲学。未知以为如何？","index":4,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"751276ee83","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":5,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"d23e59abc7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"5b83b56c22","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年二月二十八日关于国家预算的指示","index":7,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"0da330bd95","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五四年六月）增产、节约、多留后备力量，是巩固国家预算的可靠的三道防线。","index":8,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"}],"page":{"id":"8047612be8","publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb","start":51,"end":51}},"maoquanji34":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"268530614b","type":"paragraph","text":"1954年，毛泽东在杭州。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"7307ff6029","type":"subtitle","text":"防线。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"b613657c01","type":"paragraph","text":"增产、节约、多留后备力量，是巩固国家预算的可靠的三道","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"},{"id":"efc9dfca0a","type":"title","text":"关于国家预算的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb"}],"page":{"id":"4a8f8693d4","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"5ba9b3abcb","start":146,"end":146}}}},"__N_SSG":true}